OL,3,CCould Alderney change Guernsey
OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,FA senior Guernsey politician thinks it
OL,8,Fis time for a historic agreement that
OL,9,Fsets out the island's relationship
OL,10,Fwith Alderney to be reviewed.
OL,12,FThe deal was signed just after the
OL,13,FSecond World War in 1948 and has stood
OL,14,Ffor more than 75 years - ultimately
OL,15,Fallowing Guernsey to have control over
OL,16,FAlderney's financial affairs,
OL,17,Fincluding where its tax money is
OL,18,Finvested.
