OL,3,CCould Alderney change Guernsey
OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,F"But yes, I think it's right for a
OL,8,Freview and it should happen soon.
OL,9,FClearly, we've got an election in
OL,10,FGuernsey just around the corner next
OL,11,Fyear, so I can't see it happening this
OL,12,Fpolitical term, but it should be high
OL,13,Fup on the agenda for the new States."
OL,15,FDeputy Roffey's call follows concerns
OL,16,Ffrom Alderney residents who feel held
OL,17,Fback by a continued lack of investment
OL,18,Finto the island's airport.
