OL,3,CCould Alderney change Guernsey
OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,FSteve Roberts, one of Alderney's
OL,8,Frepresentatives in the States of
OL,9,FGuernsey, posted on X, formerly
OL,10,FTwitter last week: "Alderney arrivals
OL,11,Fclosed to due dust debris. How long do
OL,12,Fwe have to endure this as a taxpayer?
OL,13,FA dangerous neglect on a transferred
OL,14,Fservice to a full taxpaying Bailiwick.
OL,16,F"Neglect of an air service, a runway
OL,17,Fand now a tower that stands
OL,18,Fimmediately above the terminal."
