OL,3,CCould Alderney change Guernsey
OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,FAlderney resident Jeannie Cameron
OL,8,Fadds: "I think Alderney does need to
OL,9,Flook at the constitutional and
OL,10,Fpolitical situation that it is in and
OL,11,Fto partners within the Channel Islands
OL,12,Fwhich could potentially help more than
OL,13,Fsome may argue is happening now."
OL,15,FAlderney is an island that feels let
OL,16,Fdown by its closest neighbour.
OL,17,FGuernsey most senior politician, Chief
OL,18,FMinister Lyndon Trott, has made no
OL,19,Fsecret of his reluctance to invest in
OL,20,FAlderney's crumbling airport.
