OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,FIn response, Deputy Trott says that
OL,8,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,9,FCommittee is committed to maintaining
OL,10,Fa constructive relationship with the
OL,11,FStates of Alderney and wants a more
OL,12,Faffordable option for the airport
OL,13,Fdevelopment to bring back before
OL,14,FGuernsey States for debate.
OL,16,FRelations though appear more strained
OL,17,Fthan ever and some Alderney residents
OL,18,Fthink its time to turn to Jersey for
OL,19,Fsolutions.
