OL,3,CCould Alderney change Guernsey
OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,FSenior politicians from Jersey want to
OL,8,Fwork more closely with them, the
OL,9,FEconomic Development Minister Kirsten
OL,10,FMorel visiting Alderney earlier this
OL,11,Fmonth on an official visit.
OL,13,FAlderney States Members say the
OL,14,Fmeeting was very positive but the
OL,15,Freality is that the island's economy
OL,16,Fis struggling - pretty much all of tax
OL,17,Fmoney still goes to Guernsey.
