OL,3,CCould Alderney change Guernsey
OL,4,Crelationship and strengthen Jersey
OL,5,Cties?
OL,7,FIt needs friends like Jersey
OL,8,Fpoliticians who could put pressure on
OL,9,FGuernsey to invest more in Alderney's
OL,10,Finfrastructure.
OL,12,FPeople like Jersey Chief Minister
OL,13,FLyndon Farnham who I understand was on
OL,14,Fholiday in Alderney over the weekend
OL,15,Fand had a lovely time, including sea
OL,16,Fswimming.
